Description:
    Generates a blog that supports twitter and facebook sharing, disqus
    comments, blog wide search, tags and is build upon the box framework.

Example:
    `rails generate cms:component:blog`

    CMS: obj_class Blog
    CMS: obj_class BlogEntry
    CMS: attribute title (string)
    CMS: attribute blog_entry_tags (string)
    CMS: attribute blog_entry_author_id (string)
    CMS: attribute blog_disqus_shortname (string)
    CMS: attribute blog_entry_truncation (integer)
    CMS: attribute blog_entry_publication_date (string)
    CMS: attribute blog_enable_twitter_button (boolean)
    CMS: attribute blog_enable_disqus_comments (boolean)
    CMS: attribute blog_enable_facebook_button (boolean)
    Gems: will_paginate
    Misc: updates app/assets/javascripts/application.js
    Misc: updates config/application.rb